date:      2026-07-19
commit:    6b80cc9 (parent of bf84554 "chore: point repository field at imazen/zenav1-aom")
host:      dev-32gb
nproc:     16
rustc:     1.97.0 (2d8144b78 2026-07-07)
cargo:     1.97.0 (c980f4866 2026-06-30)
cache:     none (RUSTC_WRAPPER unset, RUSTC_WORKSPACE_WRAPPER unset, sccache not installed)

Commands (each into a fresh, separate CARGO_TARGET_DIR, run sequentially so
timings do not contend):

  rm -rf $TD && /usr/bin/time -f "LABEL|%e|%U" env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=$TD \
    cargo build --release -p zenav1-aom-dsp
  rm -rf $TD && /usr/bin/time -f "LABEL|%e|%U" env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=$TD \
    cargo build --release -p zenav1-aom --no-default-features --features decode
  rm -rf $TD && /usr/bin/time -f "LABEL|%e|%U" env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=$TD \
    cargo build --release -p zenav1-aom --no-default-features --features encode
  rm -rf $TD && /usr/bin/time -f "LABEL|%e|%U" env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=$TD \
    cargo build --release -p zenav1-aom
  rm -rf $TD && /usr/bin/time -f "LABEL|%e|%U" env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=$TD \
    cargo build --release -p archmage                      # dependency floor

  # aom-dsp solo (deps warm): touch crates/aom-dsp/src/lib.rs, rebuild -p zenav1-aom-dsp

%e = wall seconds, %U = user CPU seconds. Library-only builds: no dev-dependencies,
so zenav1-aom-sys-ref (the sole build.rs, the C oracle) is never built and no C is
compiled.

LOC counts: find <crate>/src -name '*.rs' | xargs cat | wc -l
Module cross-reference: grep -rhoE 'aom_dsp::[a-z_]+' crates/<consumer>/src/ | sort | uniq -c
